➜波兰建设新冠“临时医院”
http://www.sohu.com/a/432398158_267106	22105
<p><img src="//p9.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201117/5aa68c6774ad4f6a99428aaf2c7f62e2.jpeg" /></p>
